      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, functional option for those prioritizing utility over aesthetics. The exterior has noticeable wear, including several minor scratches and some fading on the hood and roof, and the interior shows signs of regular use with some staining on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it may require some minor maintenance or suspension work in the near future to stay in top shape. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable daily driver at an accessible price point.",
