      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This distinguished vehicle offers a superior blend of performance and sophisticated engineering. Meticulously maintained and subjected to a comprehensive multi-point inspection, it presents in commendable aesthetic and mechanical order. The interior remains refined, while the powertrain delivers the consistent, reliable output expected of a vehicle in this class. An exceptional opportunity for the professional seeking a dependable yet prestigious driving experience.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
